      "asbval:note": "Paper discusses GSEA/FGSEA for pathway enrichment analysis, but no mention of GESECA, PCA dimensionality reduction, GSE200250 dataset, or comparison of full vs reduced matrix results. The paper focuses on improving GSEA P-value estimation accuracy, not on validating dimensionality reduction effects on enrichment results.",
