    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/card/task_003/scope_drift",
      "@type": "asbval:ScopeDriftAssertion",
      "asbval:drift_notes": [
        "The candidate card describes a task involving GESECA (Gene Set Enrichment analysis on Correlation And covariance), PCA dimensionality reduction, and validation of enrichment preservation across reduced dimensions. The paper is about FGSEA (Fast Gene Set Enrichment Analysis), which focuses on improving P-value estimation accuracy for standard GSEA, not on GESECA or dimensionality reduction effects.",
        "The paper's scope is methodological improvement of GSEA P-value calculation, not validation of enrichment robustness to dimensionality reduction.",
        "The specific dataset (GSE200250) and analysis design (full vs 10-PC reduced matrix comparison) are not mentioned in the paper.",
        "Most tools listed (GEOquery, limma, ggplot2, data.table, msigdbr) are not mentioned in the provided passages and appear to be part of a typical RNA-seq analysis workflow, not the focus of this FGSEA methods paper."
      ],
      "asbval:n_drift_notes": 4,
      "asbval:target_artifact_id": "task_003",
      "asbval:target_artifact_kind": "card",
      "prov:wasAttributedTo": "anthropic/claude-haiku-4-5-20251001",
      "prov:wasGeneratedAtTime": "2026-06-15T19:25:58.220446+00:00",
      "sepio:credibility_status": {
        "@id": "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/SEPIO_0000339"
      }
    },
