      "asbval:note": "Paper focuses on P-value estimation accuracy and computational speed of FGSEA, not on result interpretation, visualization, or downstream analysis workflows. The card's research question describes post-hoc interpretation and visualization tasks (sorting, plotting, table generation), which are not the paper's primary contribution. Paper is about the computational method itself, not its application to interpret results.",
