      "asbval:note": "Paper describes fast preranked GSEA with P-value estimation (Monte-Carlo implied by 'estimate arbitrarily low P-values'), but does not explicitly mention 'adaptive' Monte-Carlo or 'geseca()' for multi-condition scoring. The paper focuses on preranked GSEA for pathway enrichment in general, not specifically multi-condition coregulation scoring.",
